    <h1 style="text-align:center;">Fiscal Year 2025 Internal Help Desk Operations Plan</h1>
    <img src="helpdesk_icon.png" alt="IT Help Desk Icon">
    
    <div class="section">
        <h2>Introduction</h2>
        <p>Hello! My name is <strong>Jaspreet Singh</strong>, and I am the Help Desk Supervisor for our internal IT Support Team. This plan outlines our operational goals and improvement strategies for the upcoming fiscal year to enhance our teamâ€™s performance, service quality, and user satisfaction.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
        <h2>Reason for the Plan</h2>
        <p>The purpose of this Operations Plan is to provide a clear roadmap for improving help desk efficiency, customer satisfaction, and service delivery standards. This plan is designed for the upcoming fiscal year to ensure measurable progress and alignment with organizational objectives.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
        <h2>Mission</h2>
        <p>Our mission is to deliver reliable, high-quality, and user-focused IT support services that empower all employees to work efficiently. We aim to resolve issues quickly, communicate clearly, and ensure every user interaction adds value to the organization.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
        <h2>Vision</h2>
        <p>To become a proactive, technology-driven support center recognized for excellence, innovation, and outstanding customer experience by the end of 2025.</p>
    </div>

    <hr>

    <div class="section">
        <h2>SMART Goals for 2025</h2>

        <div class="goal">
            <h3>Goal 1: Customer Satisfaction</h3>
            <p>Increase Customer Satisfaction Level by <strong>5%</strong> by <strong>December 31, 2025</strong> through improved resolution quality, enhanced agent communication, and faster follow-up on unresolved tickets.</p>
            <p class="benefit">User Benefit: Users will enjoy faster, clearer, and more helpful responses, improving their overall support experience.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="goal">
            <h3>Goal 2: First Contact Resolution</h3>
            <p>Increase First Contact Resolution Rate by <strong>4%</strong> by <strong>December 31, 2025</strong> through better training, enhanced knowledge base, and Tier 1 agent empowerment.</p>
            <p class="benefit">User Benefit: Fewer callbacks or escalations, saving users time and ensuring quicker problem resolution.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="goal">
            <h3>Goal 3: Abandonment Rate</h3>
            <p>Reduce Abandon Before Answer Rate by <strong>2%</strong> by <strong>December 31, 2025</strong> by improving call routing, flexible staffing, and implementing call-back options.</p>
            <p class="benefit">User Benefit: Reduced wait times and quicker access to help desk agents during busy hours.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="goal">
            <h3>Goal 4: SLA Compliance</h3>
            <p>Increase Service Level Achievement for high-priority incidents by <strong>6%</strong> by <strong>December 31, 2025</strong> through optimized prioritization, improved escalation paths, and automated SLA alerts.</p>
            <p class="benefit">User Benefit: Ensures critical issues are handled on time, minimizing downtime and disruptions.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="goal">
            <h3>Goal 5: Speed to Answer</h3>
            <p>Reduce Average Speed to Answer by <strong>10%</strong> by <strong>June 30, 2025</strong> through better call forecasting, optimized staffing, and IVR routing.</p>
            <p class="benefit">User Benefit: Faster connections to agents and improved first impressions of IT support accessibility.</p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <hr>

